xorg-server
------------------------------------------
X.Org servers

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.5-1
  libbz2_1-1.0.5-10
  libfontenc1-1.0.5-1
  libfreetype6-2.3.12-1
  libgcc1-4.3.4-3
  libgcrypt11-1.4.1-4
